    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835470/extras/bd9db71fb054f15d78afa8a11385f34d.avif?t=1725874165\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br><strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Megapotter（混合了大富翁和哈利波特的机制）：你的选择很重要，新的魔法力量是由你击败BOSS后的决定决定的。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835470/extras/704024568c61289f13aef384d0107494.poster.avif?t=1725874165\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835470/extras/704024568c61289f13aef384d0107494.webm?t=1725874165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835470/extras/704024568c61289f13aef384d0107494.mp4?t=1725874165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>使用chickendor（防御和能力）或defythering（攻击）法术力量进行游戏，或这两种类型的平衡（传说中的谣言说有可能使用所有）。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835470/extras/2f7a59fed4e3c999ab38b6e7eadf3807.poster.avif?t=1725874165\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835470/extras/2f7a59fed4e3c999ab38b6e7eadf3807.webm?t=1725874165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835470/extras/2f7a59fed4e3c999ab38b6e7eadf3807.mp4?t=1725874165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835470/extras/f088e2fc9e8861f2a2b708d596e767a2.poster.avif?t=1725874165\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835470/extras/f088e2fc9e8861f2a2b708d596e767a2.webm?t=1725874165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835470/extras/f088e2fc9e8861f2a2b708d596e767a2.mp4?t=1725874165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>只有使用确定类型的魔法才能到达的隐藏路径。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835470/extras/7f026fee010c6ccba969712ccf14815f.poster.avif?t=1725874165\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835470/extras/7f026fee010c6ccba969712ccf14815f.webm?t=1725874165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835470/extras/7f026fee010c6ccba969712ccf14815f.mp4?t=1725874165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>24个充满挑战的区域（20个主要区域+4个可解锁的可选奖励区域）。<br></li><li>16个可解锁的魔法力量。8个chickendor和8个defythering法术。<br></li><li>带有探索元素的复古风格游戏。<br></li><li>复古风格的像素艺术，声音和音乐。<br></li><li>动漫美学。<br></li><li>隐藏的物品、升级和宝藏!</li></ul></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835470/extras/f8c4f4ed730b87c1e975979f5f546a3e.avif?t=1725874165\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835470/extras/65e12eebecc1e25090b1eed86d25b890.poster.avif?t=1725874165\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835470/extras/65e12eebecc1e25090b1eed86d25b890.webm?t=1725874165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835470/extras/65e12eebecc1e25090b1eed86d25b890.mp4?t=1725874165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>这款游戏是向经典复古游戏致敬的探索元素。使用防御性/能力或进攻性魔法和过度判断的帽子，帮助小女巫Sukie打败扫帚帮女巫。你学到的新法术取决于你在游戏中的决定，因为你可以遵循新塞勒姆的古老魔法派别之一的方式。Chickendor和Defythering。当然，你可以使用这两种类型的魔法的平衡来玩这个旅程。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835470/extras/e65834d24424a4608b3e922dbce54e10.avif?t=1725874165\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>你将扮演Sukie，一个新塞勒姆巫术学校的巫师学徒。你将得到一件丢失的稀有魔法文物--过度判断帽（又名Chapeletta）的帮助。<br><br>Sukie需要证明自己的清白，并打败Broom Gang，这是一群偷盗稀有魔法物品的非法女巫。在她的旅程中，她需要遵循新塞勒姆的两个主要旧团体之一的道路。Chickendor（适合和平但胆小的女巫）或Defythering（适合勇敢但冲动的女巫）。",
